{"tid":933511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓梓亮TL原名叫『梁家進』未出道因「肛交勒索案」罪成入獄26個月","createTime":"2018-12-08T15:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T16:25:09.000Z","uid":22349,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9940c686d0d2a76da51062dd5d1a7991f599ddbd","tid":933511,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"韓梓亮、梁家進、梁迪斯、梁柏廷，到底哪一個才是真名？TL說：「我原名叫『梁家進』，到2011年爸爸有啲毛病，就嚟過身，我嗰時簽咗公司就嚟出道，公司就帶咗我去睇相，改咗『梁迪斯』，連身份證都改埋。」身份證改名為爸爸沖喜後，他又與當時唱片公司商討用「梁柏廷」作出道藝名，可惜未出道就因「肛交勒索案」罪成入獄26個月。刑滿後，他又改名「韓梓亮」：「今次冇睇相，我好鍾意韓國，『梓』就係木加個辛字，好似人只要努力就會建立到一舊木，努力就會發光發熱。」"},{"pid":"8977f62c2904bcc7cf0a8d9b7891a61a76bca401","tid":933511,"uid":22349,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160602/photo/bkn-20160602001220872-0602_00862_001_01p.jpg?20160602020620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160602%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160602001220872-0602_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20160602020620&h=8c61e1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160602/photo/bkn-20160602001220872-0602_00862_001_02p.jpg?20160602020620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160602%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160602001220872-0602_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20160602020620&h=d47f4885&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d75e3e6c8a641c37aafe6c14279483d4a72d727","tid":933511,"uid":14374,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"更生歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342d0d3a4ddb872db8f314b9a50dd1b5a8aa12ee","tid":933511,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"好想同佢玩到喘氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d194170e85952468eeaa80566ffd8779326e31","tid":933511,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  俾佢屌屎忽"},{"pid":"0a7f9747bbc27a9aac91a16f0cdac29448d2b20b","tid":933511,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"韓子亮留言疑輕生　好友綠魔許嘉浩：暫時冇事<br />\n<br />\n歌手韓子亮日前在社交平台留言疑似有輕生念頭說：「對唔住各位，或者離開世界可能真係一個解脫，我諗今次係我最後一次上社交平台！」甫文一出嚇親不少身邊好友，記者未能聯絡上子亮，但他其中一位好友許嘉浩（Karl），昨日親自打電話去了解事件，與子亮合作拍節目的Karl稱：「佢最近情緒有啲波動，佢唔止第一次類似嘅甫文，前幾日有飲過嘢，都有同佢傾偈，我哋都搵咗佢家人問候，暫時冇事！」"},{"pid":"c662067e27b712fd9a0903d92e025e020c6063d7","tid":933511,"uid":22349,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"89d194170e85952468eeaa80566ffd8779326e31","tid":933511,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  俾佢屌屎忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bimg.hitttt.com/dd8_20160309/9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbimg.hitttt.com%2Fdd8_20160309%2F9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg&h=9a28cd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到 13年被男同志雞姦，韓梓亮不禁流眼淚，喊住謂：「真係好痛。」"},{"pid":"42876f04ecba92e0f0ba657800292fe73bb34678","tid":933511,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"MaxB"},{"pid":"1a6107927bd9757b53d4e0480ab4a28cca69c181","tid":933511,"uid":31323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T20:02:30.000Z","msg":"條友當年衰咩入冊<br />\n唔好屈我00後<br />\n呢條暗星我諗冇乜幾多人識"},{"pid":"6877771bfd9b27c3dd1ec49c78fbb56478485b11","tid":933511,"uid":103230,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9940c686d0d2a76da51062dd5d1a7991f599ddbd","tid":933511,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:06:3